> flaps and bought a new coil. Replaced and still no spark. Next step was to 
> run
> a wire from the positive terminal of battery to the pos side of coil. Horn
> starts honking so have power.


> She is hooked up to the battery charger right now is not taking the 
> charge, so
> this is one dead battery.
